{"tid":2059797,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★深圳婦家中被雷劈 四成皮膚燒傷","createTime":"2020-06-11T07:27:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T07:31:51.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"49724ab7bbf657e4e618685367d348fad24a0f74","tid":2059797,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:27:59.000Z","msg":"喺屋企都會被雷劈中！深圳上周六雷雨交加，寶安區西鄉流塘社區一名50歲姓周女子在家中廚房準備煮晚飯時，突然被雷劈中，導致全身約四成皮膚燒傷，傷勢集中於面部、雙手、雙腳及腹部，燒傷程度達三級，暫無生命危險。周女姓曾女兒亦受波及，小腿灼傷，眉毛和頭髮燒焦。<br />\n<br />\n周女形容，事發時只見有個火球從窗外衝進來，自己瞬間被擊中，倒在廚房門邊。曾女則指，雷電造成的衝擊波相當強烈，連大門都飛脫，撞向對面屋。當地相關部門調查後，初步認為雷電擊中廚房窗外防盜鐵欄上方的擋雨鐵皮，形成「球狀閃電」，隨氣流入屋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E5%A9%A6%E5%AE%B6%E4%B8%AD%E8%A2%AB%E9%9B%B7%E5%8A%88-%E5%9B%9B%E6%88%90%E7%9A%AE%E8%86%9A%E7%87%92%E5%82%B7-222229?fbclid=IwAR0-srxu7ZW3v0b7PO5KPspiqjEByeQ77ht8VrBCoqDQGAToCM5wtuhn8Cg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E5%259C%25B3%25E5%25A9%25A6%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E9%259B%25B7%25E5%258A%2588-%25E5%259B%259B%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%259A%25AE%25E8%2586%259A%25E7%2587%2592%25E5%2582%25B7-222229%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0-srxu7ZW3v0b7PO5KPspiqjEByeQ77ht8VrBCoqDQGAToCM5wtuhn8Cg&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjROzsNYmc6RwURZU94nRINXI%3D&h=0ca094b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E5%A9%A6%E5%AE%B6%E4%B8%AD%E8%A2%AB%E9%9B%B7%E5%8A%88-%E5%9B%9B%E6%88%90%E7%9A%AE%E8%86%9A%E7%87%92%E5%82%B7-222229?fbclid=IwAR0-srxu7ZW3v0b7PO5KPspiqjEByeQ77ht8VrBCoqDQGAToCM5wtuhn8Cg</a>"},{"pid":"8b606fdb44c83a9b8ce6b60dee9fe41bf4cce47d","tid":2059797,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:28:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2020/6/1591715729_vK-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.clou